<div style="padding:0.2em 0.4em; line-height:1.2em;"><a href="/wiki/Revolutionary_Insurrectionary_Army_of_Ukraine" title="Revolutionary Insurrectionary Army of Ukraine">Revolutionary Insurrectionary Army of Ukraine</a></div>
