<li><a href="http://osulibrary.orst.edu/specialcollections/events/1995chomsky/index.html" class="external text" title="http://osulibrary.orst.edu/specialcollections/events/1995chomsky/index.html" rel="nofollow">Prospects for World Order</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ava_Helen_Pauling" title="Ava Helen Pauling">Ava Helen</a> and <a href="/wiki/Linus_Pauling" title="Linus Pauling">Linus Pauling</a> Memorial Lecture for Peace, <a href="/wiki/Oregon_State_University" title="Oregon State University">Oregon State University</a>, October 24, 1995. (Transcribed flash video)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ratm.com/new2/dvd_transcripts.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ratm.com/new2/dvd_transcripts.html" rel="nofollow">Interview</a> about <a href="/wiki/North_American_Free_Trade_Agreement" title="North American Free Trade Agreement">NAFTA</a>, by <a href="/wiki/Zack_de_la_Rocha" title="Zack de la Rocha">Zack de la Rocha</a> as part of the <a href="/wiki/The_Battle_of_Mexico_City" title="The Battle of Mexico City">The Battle of Mexico City</a> video, 1999 (transcript)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=1010012" class="external text" title="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=1010012" rel="nofollow">Noam Chomsky on "Talk of the Nation"; interviewed by Ray Suarez</a>, January 20, 1999</li>
<li><a href="http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0205/30/ltm.01.html" class="external text" title="http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0205/30/ltm.01.html" rel="nofollow">CNN Debate</a>, Noam Chomsky vs. <a href="/wiki/William_Bennett" title="William Bennett">Bill Bennett</a>, May 30, 2002 (transcript)</li>
<li><a href="http://frontrow.bc.edu/program/chomsky/" class="external text" title="http://frontrow.bc.edu/program/chomsky/" rel="nofollow">Talk and Q&amp;A at Boston College</a>, March 23, 2003 (<a href="/wiki/RealVideo" title="RealVideo">RealVideo</a>)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.booktv.org/feature/index.asp?segid=3562&amp;schedID=195" class="external text" title="http://www.booktv.org/feature/index.asp?segid=3562&amp;schedID=195" rel="nofollow">C-SPAN Book TV In-Depth</a>, 3-hour interview from June 1, 2003 (<a href="/wiki/RealVideo" title="RealVideo">RealVideo</a>)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=1512542" class="external text" title="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=1512542" rel="nofollow">Noam Chomsky on The Tavis Smiley Show</a>, November 19, 2003</li>
<li><a href="http://media5.bloomberg.com:443/cgi-bin/getavfile.cgi?A=22615137" class="external text" title="http://media5.bloomberg.com:443/cgi-bin/getavfile.cgi?A=22615137" rel="nofollow">Noam Chomsky on Charlie Rose</a>, November 20, 2003 (<a href="/wiki/RealAudio" title="RealAudio">RealAudio</a>)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ed.ac.uk/explore/video/chomsky.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ed.ac.uk/explore/video/chomsky.html" rel="nofollow">Noam Chomsky lecture at the University of Edinburgh</a>, March 22, 2005</li>
<li><a href="http://iopforum.harvard.edu:8080/ramgen/fr112905israel.rm" class="external text" title="http://iopforum.harvard.edu:8080/ramgen/fr112905israel.rm" rel="nofollow">John F. Kennedy School of Government Israel-Palestine Debate</a> Noam Chomsky V <a href="/wiki/Alan_Dershowitz" title="Alan Dershowitz">Alan Dershowitz</a>, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2005-11-29"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="11-29"><a href="/wiki/November_29" title="November 29">November 29</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2005" title="2005">2005</a></span>. (Real Player video)</li>
